OL,5, As the hospitality industry reels from 
OL,6, the impact of new Covid curbs, pubs and
OL,7, restaurants have reported a wave of    
OL,8, Christmas cancellations.               
OL,10,FThe Bar 44 chain, which has four       
OL,11,Foutlets, told the BBC 3,200 people had 
OL,12,Fscrapped bookings for December.        
OL,14,FNatalie Isaac, its operations director,
OL,15,Fsaid only a "handful" of people would  
OL,16,Fhave cancelled before the pandemic.    
OL,18,FOthers say that although they face no  
OL,19,Fnew rules, public caution is causing   
OL,20,Flower footfall and a loss of trade.    
